%% Visual language (inspired by high-design systems like those in awesome-design-md / DESIGN.md collections): sovereign ritual atmosphere on warm paper; Swiss "越大越细，越小越粗" typography; core as data sovereign with strong IKB border; layers as consistent supporting groups; ritual edges as the deliberate design interventions that close the emotional asset loop. Structure > decoration, grid-aligned, geometry focus.
%% Follows mermaid-arc-skills + guizang locked mode rules + DESIGN.md "preview compatibility first" rule.
architecture-beta
    group core(database)[.md 数据主权<br/>Local-first<br/>被动 AI（用户导出调用）<br/>完整归档]

    group money(cloud)[Money 量化台账]
    service daily[日均成本计算] in money
    service dates[buyDate vs startDate 分离] in money
    service sell[卖出结算闭环] in money

    group knowledge(cloud)[Knowledge 闪念采集]
    service notes[Markdown-native 笔记] in knowledge
    service meta[使用元数据关联] in knowledge
    service zettlr[Zettlr 桌面协同] in knowledge

    group sentiment(cloud)[Sentiment 仪式回响]
    service trigger[仅里程碑触发] in sentiment
    service guide[购入引导 + 卖出告别] in sentiment
    service peak[情感峰值补偿] in sentiment

    %% Closed emotional asset loop — the intentional design intervention
    core -->|购入仪式 引导| money
    money -->|持有 日常量化 + 时间感知| core
    core -->|里程碑触发 仪式| sentiment
    sentiment -->|卖出告别 情感归档| core
    core -->|闪念采集 被动| knowledge
    knowledge -->|元数据重组 导出调用| core

    classDef coreCore fill:#f5f0eb,stroke:#002FA7,stroke-width:2px,color:#1B365D
    classDef layerGroup fill:#f0f0ee,stroke:#a8a29e,color:#44403c

    class core coreCore
    class money,knowledge,sentiment layerGroup